&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DevOps Engineer (Data &amp;amp; AI Platform)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;We are hiring a DevOps Engineer to support and scale our Data and AI platform in production. This role focuses on building reliable infrastructure for data pipelines and ML systems, standardizing deployment patterns, and ensuring performance, observability, and cost efficiency across compute-intensive workloads.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Build and operate infrastructure for data pipelines and AI/ML workloads&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain CI/CD for application and model lifecycle (build, train, deploy)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Manage Infrastructure as Code (Terraform) across environments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Support containerized workloads and orchestration (Docker, Kubernetes)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Partner with Machine Learning teams and engineering to productionize models&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Implement monitoring, logging, and tracing for data flow and model performance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Improve reliability, scalability, and cost efficiency of data systems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Enforce security and access controls for data and infrastructure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Reduce operational overhead through automation and tooling&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;3+ years of experience in DevOps, SRE, or infrastructure engineering&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;End-to-End MLOps/LLMOps Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Experience deploying and maintaining ML/AI workflows. Familiarity with the unique nature of promoting AI assets (models, datasets, and code) through the lifecycle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Strong cloud experience (AWS preferred)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Proficiency with Terraform (or similar IaC tools)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Experience with Docker and Kubernetes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Familiarity with CI/CD and Git-based workflows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;The Executive Assistant provides comprehensive administrative and operational support to the CFO and CPO. This pivotal role spans traditional EA excellence: calendars, travel, events and the operational infrastructure both teams depend on: meeting rhythms, initiative tracking, and OKR accountability. The right person actively uses AI to eliminate routine work while being a strong culture facilitator.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are hiring for two Executive Assistant roles, one to support the Finance and People &amp;amp; Culture teams and another to support GTM, Customer Success, and Clinical Strategy. While this description reflects the scope for Finance and People, we welcome candidates with a range of EA experience and backgrounds to apply.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Administrative Support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Proactively manage calendars and travel for both executives, anticipating conflicts, protecting focus time, and ensuring both are prepared for every commitment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Process expense reports accurately and on time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meeting Infrastructure &amp;amp; Facilitation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Own agendas for all leadership and full-team meetings — gather topics in advance, synthesize priorities, and distribute pre-reads.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Facilitate leadership meetings; capture decisions in real time and maintain a living action item log with owners and due dates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Surface open items and follow through to closure without being asked.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Initiative Tracking &amp;amp; OKRs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Maintain a living tracker of key initiatives across both orgs — flag risks and delays before they become surprises.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Own OKR submission and review cycles; hold leaders accountable for timely inputs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Keep core documents current: OKRs, strategic priorities, and operating frameworks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Enabled Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;color: #000000 !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Automate repetitive work using AI — meeting summaries, agenda drafts, status reports, and follow-up tracking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
