&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Your work will focus on the semantic and component token layer of our design system alongside our engineering team. In practice, that might mean spending an afternoon defining spacing and typography tokens with a design systems engineer, a few days later prototyping a component pattern in Figma Make, and the following week documenting governance standards that the rest of the design org will rely on. The common thread across all of it is the seam between design intent and engineering execution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
